{"tid":2235771,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾入理大陪學生離開　曾鈺成指當時有人言論涼薄","createTime":"2020-10-09T03:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T03:09:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5f4a7911c960b6e861aaadd5bb84fbf95860c1b0","tid":2235771,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:02:39.000Z","msg":"立法會前主席曾鈺成在本台節目《鏗鏘說》表示，建制派不同意他處理「拉布」的手法，但他指出，議員在《議事規則》內拉布，是少數派抗衡的唯一手段，在英式議會文化中，要容許甚至要支持有關行為。不過及後政府、建制派及其支持者都認為，「拉布」是「垃圾」，一分鐘都不應該。<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成去年11月反修例風波期間，曾進入被警方包圍的理工大學校園，陪同部分學生離開。他提到當晚的年輕人都很絕望，入校園時無想過不能出去，他與部分人傾談期間，曾有一些年輕人問及如跟隨離開校園，會否被告暴動罪。曾鈺成認為，坊間有人不考慮該批學生的情況，就指責誰人「食人血饅頭」或誰人「有著數」，他說明白當時有選舉即將舉行，但認為有關言論涼薄。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553779-20201009.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553779-20201009.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=b165e556\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553779-20201009.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=67318fed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553779-20201009.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"25a00a11e97a9ef72606232ec5fd29d22f78eda1","tid":2235771,"uid":7323,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:04:52.000Z","msg":"你入去係帶朱媛走"},{"pid":"292fe8ef64da0e682b2a0087587f04144077c8d3","tid":2235771,"uid":240347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">朱媛呢 ??</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78450120815dd61fd621d55c6671c3d0f0add7f","tid":2235771,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:06:36.000Z","msg":"鄧炳強、李家超、梁振英<br />\n日日話人為「政治紅利」、食「人血饅頭」"},{"pid":"a7cd4fb996af1dcaab388bd1eb8fa5d3554ec922","tid":2235771,"uid":204539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:06:54.000Z","msg":"主持有無問朱媛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970a85a3c00c02fa7942723b7ea66bb53b36ee17","tid":2235771,"uid":127929,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:06:59.000Z","msg":"陪學生離開?陪你老母咩，曾鈺成你係呃學生出去死呀，<br />\n<br />\n個班未成年乜都冇做過既既比狗非法禁固左幾日出返黎，<br />\n<br />\n第二朝咪又係比狗上門拉暴動，屌你老母去死啦曾鈺成係度扮好人，好假呀你，專心揾你既朱緩去性交啦"},{"pid":"f6abb6c8f3a3fa971acdccede5a13470147f7beb","tid":2235771,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:09:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}